I'll just borrow an EEG 10
from some lab and modify it.

27:07.798 --> 27:09.179
Borrow an EEG 10?

27:10.594 --> 27:12.182
Yeah.

27:12.216 --> 27:13.216
Eden.

27:14.218 --> 27:15.668
- What?
- You heard me.

27:17.359 --> 27:20.915
- Eden's just a myth.
- Tell that to Nicola.

27:20.949 --> 27:22.824
Nicola was selfish, it
could have been anybody.

27:22.848 --> 27:24.228
- Selfish?
- Yeah.

27:25.402 --> 27:27.335
Nicola was a fucking genius,

27:27.369 --> 27:28.992
you have no idea what
was motivating her.

27:29.026 --> 27:30.306
