27:31.857 --> 27:34.791
Whether you like it or not,
your history is my history.

27:38.311 --> 27:40.037
I'm losing my fucking mind.

27:41.383 --> 27:42.868
Nicola's headset is key.

27:43.834 --> 27:45.111
You borrow some EEG 10

27:45.146 --> 27:47.148
and they'll be on you
like pigs in shit.

27:47.182 --> 27:48.736
Even if this guy is real

27:48.770 --> 27:51.152
no one has any clue
where he is, okay?

27:52.705 --> 27:57.192
Mason, fear and morality
and every other human concept

27:57.227 --> 27:58.884
in the world will
become irrelevant

27:58.918 --> 28:00.195
once we have that headset.

28:02.301 --> 28:04.406
If there's anyone that
can do it, it's us.

28:06.408 --> 28:07.408
Donezo!

28:24.392 --> 28:26.463
Zip!

28:26.497 --> 28:28.223
I love you, man!

28:28.258 --> 28:29.846
I knew you wouldn't let me down.

28:31.019 --> 28:33.435
Yo, who you been
talking to, man?

28:34.851 --> 28:36.093
Me, dickhead.

28:36.128 --> 28:39.648
Honestly, my
imaginary projection.

28:42.479 --> 28:44.723
Oh word, okay, what's his name?

28:44.757 --> 28:47.656
- Finn.
- Finn and Mason?

28:47.691 --> 28:50.142
