clothing store.

28:53.870 --> 28:54.802
I got something else for you.

28:54.836 --> 28:56.320
Oh, yeah what's that?

28:56.355 --> 28:58.771
Ooh, you're gonna owe
me big time for this one.

28:58.806 --> 29:00.255
What is it?

29:00.290 --> 29:04.743
I set up Eden's shop,
and I dropped a GPS tag.

29:09.644 --> 29:10.818
I'm gonna need a mask.

29:13.959 --> 29:15.098
Weird looking.

29:19.447 --> 29:20.966
You look like a child.

29:25.349 --> 29:28.007
I can't be seen
with you like this.

29:28.042 --> 29:30.596
I can't be seen with
you anyway, but.

29:30.630 --> 29:31.666
I like it.

29:31.700 --> 29:33.875
Fuck you.

29:33.910 --> 29:34.980
Fucking weirdo.

29:35.877 --> 29:37.810
No you're the fucking weirdo.

29:37.845 --> 29:39.018
We're both fucking weirdos.

29:39.053 --> 29:40.779
Let's take over
the world together.

29:41.780 --> 29:43.298
This is in your mind.

29:45.438 --> 29:47.544
I just want you to
feel right, you know.

29:53.550 --> 29:54.550
Yes.

30:38.284 --> 30:39.872
Freeze, motherfucker!

30:39.907 --> 30:41.874
Dammit, Finn!

30:41.909 --> 30:44.704
I fucking love this place.

30:44.739 --> 30:45.739
Hello!

30:46.637 --> 30:48.191
Hello!

30:48.225 --> 30:50.193
Are you not entertained?

30:53.817 --> 30:57.165
You think it's true what
they're saying about this guy?

30:57.200 --> 31:00.824
Hard to say, my man,
hard to fucking say.

31:00.859 --> 31:01.859
Pretty messed up.

31:02.964 --> 31:04.690
I've seen worse.

31:04.724 --> 31:07.313
Oh, have you?

31:07.348 --> 31:08.142
Don't presume to know
everything there is

31:08.176 --> 31:09.798
to know about me, Mason.

31:10.972 --> 31:13.733
Just don't fuck with
me in here, all right?

31:13.768 --> 31:15.666
I'm on your team, my man.

31:15.701 --> 31:18.117
There is no fucking
that I am not a part of.

31:31.993 --> 31:32.993
Shit.

31:36.411 --> 31:37.411
Think he saw us?

31:40.691 --> 31:42.210
Huh?

31:42.245 --> 31:45.317
Well he's in a nuclear bunker

31:46.283 --> 31:47.906
so I don't think
he gives a fuck.

31:49.528 --> 31:50.528
Oh, shit.

31:52.048 --> 31:54.705
Don't worry,
man, you can crack it.

31:54.740 --> 31:57.398
Zip didn't say anything
about a door with no handle.

32:02.921 --> 32:04.992
You're nervous.

32:05.026 --> 32:06.648
Of course I'm fucking nervous.

32:07.580 --> 32:09.858
You curse when you get nervous.

32:09.893 --> 32:11.860
You heard what he
said about this guy.

32:14.277 --> 32:15.726
Yeah, no, you're right,

32:15.761 --> 32:17.797
we should go home and
get the fuck out of here.

32:17.832 --> 32:19.178
Finn!

32:19.213 --> 32:21.042
I need your help on this.

32:21.077 --> 32:22.975
Sorry!

32:23.010 --> 32:24.563
Have fun!

32:24.597 --> 32:25.597
Finn!

32:26.806 --> 32:28.291
I need your help.

32:28.325 --> 32:29.325
There you go.

32:33.158 --> 32:35.505
Have you ever tried to
go somewhere I wasn't?

32:41.097 --> 32:42.097
All the time.

32:43.168 --> 32:44.203
Has it ever worked?

32:48.035 --> 32:49.035
No.

32:51.935 --> 32:52.935
Can you try?

32:54.420 --> 32:55.732
Huh?

32:55.766 --> 32:56.766
Can you try?

33:00.116 --> 33:02.359
I think that's more
on you, than it is me.

33:04.844 --> 33:05.844
Okay.

33:08.607 --> 33:09.607
Okay what?

33:10.816 --> 33:11.816
Let's do it.

33:13.957 --> 33:14.957
Okay.

33:16.339 --> 33:17.339
Let's do it!

33:19.342 --> 33:20.342
Let's do what?

33:21.654 --> 33:22.862
Transcendence, man.

33:25.003 --> 33:26.935
You're out of your fucking mind.

33:26.970 --> 33:29.386
No, you're out of my mind.

33:35.392 --> 33:36.497
Okay, what do we do?

33:39.534 --> 33:41.812
Well we know from quantum
physics that time and space

33:41.847 --> 33:43.711
are only relative
to our perspective.

33:45.092 --> 33:47.128
We need to see
that room so wholly

33:47.163 --> 33:51.719
in our mind's eye you'll
actually be there.

33:53.617 --> 33:58.622
Okay.

34:00.383 --> 34:06.078
The room is square,
20 feet by 20 feet.

34:06.113 --> 34:07.183
The walls are silver.

34:09.116 --> 34:10.978
In the center of
the room is a chair.

34:12.739 --> 34:16.433
Inside that chair is
a guy called Eden.

34:22.750 --> 34:23.750
Holy shit.

34:28.273 --> 34:29.273
Finn?!

34:30.654 --> 34:32.242
- Mason.
- Finn?!

34:34.141 --> 34:36.246
- I'm inside.
- No?!

34:37.799 --> 34:38.799
What's happening?

34:44.668 --> 34:45.668
Shit.

34:50.880 --> 34:53.091
Looks like he's
digitizing his brain.

34:53.125 --> 34:54.746
Shit!

34:54.782 --> 34:55.782
Is he asleep?

34:56.922 --> 34:57.922
Catatonic.

34:59.027 --> 35:00.419
Shit, this is the
last puzzle piece!

35:00.443 --> 35:01.375
Is there a door?

35:01.409 --> 35:02.479
An alarm?

35:07.312 --> 35:08.554
No, there's no way out.

35:09.659 --> 35:10.981
It must be voice
activated or something.

35:11.005 --> 35:12.005
Think!

35:14.146 --> 35:15.596
This is our last chance, man.

35:23.983 --> 35:24.983
Mason?

35:26.054 --> 35:27.054
Yeah?

35:33.131 --> 35:35.788
What's to say I
can't project you here?

35:42.105 --> 35:43.105
Nothing.

35:49.285 --> 35:51.563
Apart from the fact that
I'm made of physical matter

35:51.597 --> 35:54.013
and that would be
physically impossible.

36:01.331 --> 36:02.331
Finn?

36:05.680 --> 36:06.680
Finn?

36:35.400 --> 36:36.400
Open the door.

36:41.095 --> 36:42.476
I said open the door!

36:44.650 --> 36:46.963
I'm gonna skin you
alive, you little rodent.

36:49.586 --> 36:51.830
Say the code and open the door

36:51.864 --> 36:53.280
or I will break your machine.

36:58.940 --> 36:59.940
Reckoning.

37:13.161 --> 37:14.542
You killed Nicola.

37:29.695 --> 37:33.354
If I ever see you again,
I'm gonna kill you.

38:08.976 --> 38:10.391
Hey, it's Zip,

38:10.426 --> 38:14.568
I'm not picking up my phone
ever so leave a message.

38:14.602 --> 38:19.158
Yo Zip, man, give me a call,
alright, some shit went down.

38:20.643 --> 38:21.643
Okay.

38:22.921 --> 38:23.921
Mason.

38:30.480 --> 38:31.480
Mason.

38:34.035 --> 38:35.416
Mason, Mason.

38:35.451 --> 38:36.279
Where are you?

38:36.314 --> 38:37.314
Mason.

38:49.292 --> 38:50.292
Hi.

38:55.402 --> 38:57.162
Is someone day tripping?

39:00.199 --> 39:01.199
Must be good.

39:07.724 --> 39:11.141
This area just
needed a little life.

39:15.663 --> 39:17.182
Sorry, I just...

39:20.461 --> 39:22.912
Want to see something cool?

40:13.411 --> 40:15.067
Jammers and germs.

40:18.001 --> 40:20.487
It's time to change the world.

40:28.046 --> 40:29.703
By decoding the human brain

40:29.737 --> 40:34.224
and all of it's beautiful,
terrible intricacy.

40:36.330 --> 40:38.159
I hope to discover
what might just be

40:40.161 --> 40:41.715
the spark of consciousness.

40:44.303 --> 40:45.581
The spark of life.

41:52.682 --> 41:53.682
Mason.

42:02.278 --> 42:03.278
Come here.

42:05.592 --> 42:06.592
This way.

42:10.769 --> 42:13.013
Want to see something cool?

42:17.258 --> 42:22.160
Okay, so, your brain is made
of over 80 billion neurons,

42:22.194 --> 42:23.989
none of which give
a damn about you.

42:25.163 --> 42:27.924
Now they work just like
an on and off switch.

42:29.063 --> 42:30.651
So the zillion dollar question

42:30.686 --> 42:33.274
is why did these
signals originate?

42:35.691 --> 42:39.522
No one knows, so that's
what I want to find out.

42:39.557 --> 42:41.420
So by finding out the
code of consciousness,

42:41.455 --> 42:43.630
I'll be able to find
out the original spark.

42:45.735 --> 42:47.185
Original spark of what?

42:49.843 --> 42:50.843
Of life.

42:52.949 --> 42:53.949
Wow.

42:57.402 --> 42:58.955
That's what I'm gonna rewrite.

43:00.957 --> 43:02.200
Rewrite?

43:02.234 --> 43:03.234
Yeah.

43:04.892 --> 43:06.514
Why?

43:06.549 --> 43:09.172
Because human beings are
programmed to destroy everything.

43:10.933 --> 43:13.487
- And create.
- By destruction.

43:16.870 --> 43:20.805
I know it sounds crazy, but
I've thought this through.

43:20.839 --> 43:22.738
But what if we're
flawed for a reason.

43:22.772 --> 43:24.015
We're just outdated.

43:24.049 --> 43:26.638
You realize you would
be playing God right?

43:30.987 --> 43:32.713
I've had a long
day and I don't...

43:32.748 --> 43:35.371
- Answer the question.
- I just want to fix people.

43:38.167 --> 43:41.377
But what if I don't
want my mind rewritten?

43:42.516 --> 43:43.976
What if I want to figure
life out for myself?

43:44.000 --> 43:46.554
That sounds like
a human deficiency.

43:46.589 --> 43:47.670
Free will is a deficiency?

43:47.694 --> 43:49.592
No it's not that, it's...

43:49.627 --> 43:51.456
The brain is
programmed in a very...

43:54.701 --> 43:56.254
I know what I'm doing, okay?

44:06.022 --> 44:07.022
Mason.

44:10.164 --> 44:11.407
Anyone who thinks they know

44:11.441 --> 44:14.824
the answer to life
is full of shit.

44:24.731 --> 44:25.870
I got to go.

44:59.179 --> 45:00.179
Amazing.

45:04.287 --> 45:06.289
Do you think this is it?

45:15.505 --> 45:16.714
It's the Ichor.

45:19.095 --> 45:20.856
The blood of the gods.

45:24.376 --> 45:25.376
Consciousness.

45:31.280 --> 45:33.972
Finn, wait.

45:34.007 --> 45:35.008
Finn, don't.

45:37.148 --> 45:38.148
Finn!

45:39.046 --> 45:40.046
Finn!

45:40.807 --> 45:41.807
Finn!

46:20.294 --> 46:21.294
It's gone.

46:30.857 --> 46:31.857
Mason.

46:33.721 --> 46:34.721
What?

46:42.592 --> 46:43.697
I can feel.

46:53.051 --> 46:54.881
I can feel everything.

47:28.776 --> 47:30.675
Sun Moon.

47:33.229 --> 47:36.474
So you know nothing
about this tracker?

47:40.788 --> 47:47.761
I told you, people
here do as they please.

47:47.795 --> 47:49.004
That's the whole idea.

47:51.869 --> 47:54.388
That's a beautiful way to live.

47:54.423 --> 47:58.185
Do what you please, as
long as no one gets hurt.

48:02.293 --> 48:03.950
Well I did get hurt.

48:06.987 --> 48:08.644
What do you want?

48:11.681 --> 48:15.513
I'm deeply troubled
that you don't see

48:15.547 --> 48:17.273
the irony in your own existence.

48:17.308 --> 48:25.308
You had something here, and
yet besides a few bent rules,

48:27.180 --> 48:34.187
you cling to the human law
like a pet on a long leash.

48:36.810 --> 48:39.330
Where is the revolution?

48:39.364 --> 48:42.298
Where is the reckoning?

48:46.164 --> 48:47.164
Poor man.

48:50.099 --> 48:54.690
Life itself is the reckoning.

49:03.009 --> 49:10.533
Maybe that's why my little
toy elicits such physical pain.

49:39.079 --> 49:41.116
Tell me what you want.

49:41.150 --> 49:45.327
I want you realize that
your life is meaningless

49:46.914 --> 49:51.057
and I want to know who
wears the vermin mask.

49:57.270 --> 49:58.270
Ah.

49:59.513 --> 50:00.513
You know him.

50:07.245 --> 50:08.281
Where can I find him?

50:25.160 --> 50:26.540
Tell me his name.

50:26.575 --> 50:28.577
I don't know his name.

50:35.929 --> 50:38.794
Tell me, his name.

50:52.601 --> 50:54.534
Fuck you!

51:35.989 --> 51:37.094
He's a ghost.

51:40.200 --> 51:42.340
No one knows where he is.

51:50.279 --> 51:55.250
Then it seems you no
longer have any value to me.

52:02.429 --> 52:04.949
The reckoning then.

52:31.355 --> 52:32.770
Dammit.

52:34.427 --> 52:35.807
I want food, Mason.

52:37.499 --> 52:38.534
I need food.

52:40.571 --> 52:41.744
I want a pizza.

52:43.746 --> 52:45.310
Yeah, well I've told
you we can't go anywhere

52:45.334 --> 52:47.612
until I figure out
what's going on.

52:47.647 --> 52:49.925
Mason, I don't
think you understand,

52:49.959 --> 52:51.823
I'm the hungriest man alive.

52:52.997 --> 52:54.216
Do you not care
what's happening here?

52:54.240 --> 52:55.240
I do not.

52:56.242 --> 52:57.760
We can fix it later.

52:57.795 --> 52:59.221
You have seen all the crazy
shit that's gone on, right?

52:59.245 --> 53:00.246
Yes.

53:00.280 --> 53:01.557
And now I feel...

53:03.283 --> 53:07.287
I feel like I'm going
to murder someone

53:07.322 --> 53:08.564
if I don't get some food.

53:09.979 --> 53:11.094
This whole thing is your idea

53:11.118 --> 53:13.224
so no we're not going anywhere.

53:14.639 --> 53:16.572
This piece of shit, I
think the Q chip is fried.

53:23.648 --> 53:25.029
I want girls, Mason.

53:26.582 --> 53:27.928
I want all of the girls.

53:29.896 --> 53:32.899
I want to explode inside every
single girl on this planet.

53:35.798 --> 53:38.076
Oh shit, what am I doing?

53:39.388 --> 53:41.356
- I'm going out now.
- No, you're not.

53:42.564 --> 53:45.360
I deserve it after
all I've gone through.

53:45.394 --> 53:46.602
You've gone through?

53:46.637 --> 53:48.121
You haven't felt
any of this shit.

53:49.881 --> 53:51.469
The rules have changed, Mason.

53:53.437 --> 53:55.577
What the fuck?

53:56.474 --> 53:57.855
Equal partners, my man.

53:57.889 --> 53:58.994
That's the haps.

54:03.550 --> 54:05.380
I am losing my mind.

54:06.829 --> 54:10.764
I have physically manifested
a projection from my mind.

54:13.974 --> 54:14.974
Your mind?

54:15.873 --> 54:16.805
- Yeah.
- Your mind?

54:16.839 --> 54:17.737
That's what you think?

54:17.771 --> 54:18.771
Yeah, my mind.

54:21.430 --> 54:24.399
That is exactly
the fucking problem!

54:24.433 --> 54:25.433
What is?

54:30.059 --> 54:34.167
You think I'm just like a
part of your fucking brain?

54:34.201 --> 54:35.099
Right?

54:35.133 --> 54:37.515
Like a synaptic mishap?

54:37.550 --> 54:39.310
That's what you think,
you're the genius,

54:39.345 --> 54:41.219
you're all that matters, is
that what you fucking think?

54:41.243 --> 54:43.521
I'm just trying to fix it, okay?

54:45.799 --> 54:47.663
I cannot believe
how selfish you are.

54:49.182 --> 54:51.011
- Selfish?
- Yeah.

54:51.046 --> 54:53.324
Selfish!

54:53.359 --> 54:54.739
You think I'm fucking selfish?

54:54.774 --> 54:55.774
Yeah.

54:56.741 --> 55:00.469
I am your fucking
self, you fucking idiot!

55:00.504 --> 55:03.852
I spent my entire life
on that project of yours!

55:03.886 --> 55:06.130
And now you're alive!

55:06.164 --> 55:08.960
You touched the fucking space
goo and now you're alive!

55:08.995 --> 55:11.411
That could have been
the physical embodiment

55:11.446 --> 55:14.483
of consciousness,
essentially a God,

55:14.518 --> 55:16.899
and if you've broken it
or altered it somehow,

55:16.934 --> 55:19.902
who knows what's happening
to our existence, okay?

55:19.937 --> 55:21.801
Can you get that
into your shit brain!

55:36.436 --> 55:42.131
I don't know what happened
to me or how I became real,

55:44.755 --> 55:49.760
but if this is what
broken feels like, fuck!

55:52.072 --> 55:54.247
Why would anybody want to fixed?

55:56.180 --> 55:57.871
You're the genius, Mason.

55:59.321 --> 56:00.322
You'll figure it out.

56:01.288 --> 56:02.082
Finn, Finn!

56:02.117 --> 56:03.325
Finn, wait!

56:03.360 --> 56:07.467
- Let go of me.
- You can't go.

56:08.261 --> 56:10.125
I can do whatever
the fuck I want.

56:18.444 --> 56:19.444
Wow.

56:39.326 --> 56:40.326
Hello!

56:45.056 --> 56:46.541
I'm fucking alive!

56:57.068 --> 56:58.068
Fuck.

57:00.244 --> 57:01.244
Fuck me.

58:20.255 --> 58:25.260
I'll take the purple one.

58:25.847 --> 58:26.848
Good choice.

58:39.446 --> 58:40.758
That's purple.

01:01:08.147 --> 01:01:10.390
- I need a dose.
- Mr. Vix!

01:01:23.231 --> 01:01:26.061
Have you seen a guy called Finn?

01:01:43.665 --> 01:01:44.665
Yo!

01:01:45.598 --> 01:01:46.598
Yo!

01:01:48.152 --> 01:01:49.152
Yo.

01:01:50.258 --> 01:01:51.258
Mason?

01:01:52.985 --> 01:01:54.952
I just had my first dream.

01:01:57.368 --> 01:01:59.129
Did you not just
feel what happened?

01:02:02.028 --> 01:02:03.478
What?

01:02:03.512 --> 01:02:07.724
We were glitching?

01:02:08.966 --> 01:02:10.968
Is that what that was?

01:02:16.111 --> 01:02:17.837
What the fuck, man?

01:02:19.287 --> 01:02:21.254
The map is fragmenting,
the processor is fried,

01:02:21.289 --> 01:02:22.473
and you're lying here
as high as a kite.

01:02:22.497 --> 01:02:23.670
We have to fix this!

01:02:25.396 --> 01:02:26.777
I'm taking a little break.

01:02:28.883 --> 01:02:30.677
We were just fucking glitching.

01:02:33.888 --> 01:02:37.270
Look, Eden's lab, the
Q chip is still there.

01:02:37.305 --> 01:02:38.513
Mason.

01:02:38.547 --> 01:02:39.801
I smashed the computer but
most of the hardware must be...

01:02:39.825 --> 01:02:40.825
Mason!

01:02:44.243 --> 01:02:46.590
I'm not going back down there.

01:02:47.902 --> 01:02:48.902
We have to.

